me), where I've been in melee range).<br>
<br>
As for the fire pets AoEing, there's a slight logistical problem with that. From my experience, you must have 3+ mobs attack you or pet (ie: more than 3 on your pet's hate list) before your pet will AoE. It's only a dippy 150 pt AoE at best, as well, and .. fire pets don't do it twice. It's almost as if they're AoEing to taunt mobs, and not to do damage.<br>
