<br>
Earth pets are not immune to slow, they simply have a huge resistance to it. I have seen earths get hit by shreeker slow (from mushrooms in fungus grove)<br>
<br>
do not use the big 61 bolt until the mob is at half or lower.  you will draw too much agro.  a good stratigy should be the 61+ mages nuking once each when the mob hits half to finish it.<br>
<br>
consider investing in AA to have things like pet CH at your disposal.  very useful in these fights.<br>
